This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new trainable pooling layer for deep neural networks. The paper also mentions experiments on image classification, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of the proposed layer as a regularizer, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the processing of structured data, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language).
